  "instructions": [
    "Combine noodles, butter, and a pinch of salt in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Cook, stirring frequently, until the noodles are lightly toasted and the butter has melted.",
    "Add peas, garlic, and ginger to the skillet and cook, stirring occasionally, until the peas are tender but still crisp.",
    "Add fish sauce and soy sauce to the skillet, stirring to combine. Season with black pepper to taste.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes to allow the flavors to meld together.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped scallions if desired."
